{
  "id": "019cdcdc-fd01-7d11-b0d7-9fdcb15b2308",
  "content": "## Problem\n\n### Root Cause\n\n`wire_pipeline_relations()` matched `pc.metadata.source_file == rel.to_file`, but:\n\n1. **Rust `crate::` imports**: `to_file` was set to the SOURCE file path (not the target), so every \"import\" edge pointed back at itself\n2. **Rust `super::` imports**: Same problem — `to_file = file_path` regardless of actual target\n3. **External crate imports**: `to_file = \"std::collections\"` — no match (expected, OK)\n4. **JS/TS relative imports**: `to_file = \"./utils\"` — never matches `src/utils.ts`\n",
  "source_version": "docs/rfcs/2026-03-04-m4.2-graph-relation-wiring-fix.md",
